default11
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultLack of integration: defaultmany of our client’s complaints 
defaultcross the
default health and social care 
defaultboundaries
default. PHSO does not have the remit to investigate social care complaints and therefore our clients then either need to deal with two Ombudsmen or have their complaint investigated as a ‘joint investigation’. As the two Ombudsmen sit in different locations, have different processes and different remits, this makes it very difficult for our clients and all the problems stated above are exacerbated.
